# Recall Touch — Marketing Site (Design System)

You are implementing the Recall Touch marketing website to Linear/Stripe-grade quality. Dark theme only. No light mode.

## Design tokens (use these; do not improvise)

- **Backgrounds**: `--bg-primary` #0A0A0B, `--bg-surface` #111113, `--bg-elevated` #1A1A1D
- **Borders**: `--border-default` rgba(255,255,255,0.06), `--border-hover` rgba(255,255,255,0.1)
- **Accent**: `--accent-primary` #4F8CFF (CTAs, links), `--accent-secondary` #00D4AA (status, governed)
- **Text**: `--text-primary` #EDEDEF, `--text-secondary` #8B8B8D, `--text-tertiary` #5A5A5C
- **Warning**: `--accent-warning` #FFB224
- **Container**: max-width 1200px, padding 24px / 40px / 48px by breakpoint
- **Sections**: vertical padding 80px (mobile), 120px (tablet), 160px (desktop)
- **Radius**: 12px cards, 8px buttons, 6px inputs

## Components

- **Navbar**: Sticky, backdrop-blur on scroll, 64px height. Logo + Product, Pricing, Documentation + Sign in (ghost) + Start free (primary).
- **Buttons**: `.btn-marketing-primary` (filled blue), `.btn-marketing-ghost` (border only). Large variant: `.btn-lg`.
- **Cards**: `.card-marketing` — surface bg, 1px border, 12px radius, hover border/background transition.
- **Section label**: `.section-label` — 12px uppercase, letter-spacing 0.1em, `--accent-primary` color.

## Copy voice

- Authoritative, concise. No "just", "simply", "easily", "leverage", "utilize", "revolutionary".
- The product **governs**; it doesn’t "help you manage". Use: governed, under record, auditable, compliant, infrastructure.
- No questions as headlines. Statements only.

## Homepage sections (order)

1. Navbar 2. Hero (eyebrow + H1 + subhead + CTAs + product visual) 3. Problem 4. How it works (3 steps) 5. Capabilities (bento) 6. Use cases 7. Pricing preview 8. Trust / social proof 9. Final CTA 10. Footer

## Tech

- Framer Motion: use `ease: "easeOut"` (not cubic-bezier array) for TypeScript compatibility.
- Icons: Lucide React. Fonts: Inter (body), JetBrains Mono (code/records).
- No component libraries (no shadcn, Chakra, MUI). Custom components only.
